short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: An extension that automatcally gets analytics from youtube studio for your A/B testing.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Automatically pull in data for your Youtube A/B tests without having to upload CTR, Watch Time and AVD manually. Open youtube studio once and start saving and updating your analytics.

New Feature Release (13/9/2024): 
Find tons of top-performing videos and save hours on research with Outliers and VPH! It’s super easy—just check a channel page, search page, homepage or watch page and instantly see Outliers and VPH to instantly know which videos are the standouts, no math required.
